              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>An <html:em><html:strong>equivalence</html:strong></html:em> from <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> is defined to be a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A \to  B]]></fr:tex> equipped with a  <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000U/" title="Biinverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000U/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000U/" type="local">biinverse</fr:link>.</html:p>
